  "text": "We can then solve for PA, PB, PC and obtain the 3D coordinates A I , B I , C I of A, B, C in current camera coordinates [CITATION_1] ]. This allows us to solve for R,T of the new view and similarly we apply triangulation to obtain more 3D points. We iterate this process until all images are inserted and apply one more round of bundle adjustment:",
